    "instruction": "Load metric.csv, trace.csv, log.csv, and error_logs.csv. For each file, return a compact summary only: 1) total row count; 2) minimum and maximum timestamp shown as ISO UTC datetimes; 3) up to 20 unique cmdb_id values; 4) the set of unique KPI/trace/log name values (kpi_name for metric.csv, trace_name for trace.csv, log_name for log.csv) limited to 50 items; 5) show up to 5 sample rows (all columns). Keep outputs concise and do not print entire files."
